    public class OMPanelTesting
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    Creates and shows the analysing and testing panel for this software tool. Allows the user to analyse the simulation results and to manually create virtual campaigns.
    Author:
    A. Schoedon

                                     boolean preview,
                                     boolean fullscreen)
        Creates a panel displaying the chart of the radon concentration of a virtual campaign.
        Parameters:
        campaign - The campaign object containing all rooms and radon data.
        preview - Will hide annotations, labels and headlines if true.
        fullscreen - Will correctly adjust the preferred size to screen resolution if true.
        Returns:
        A panel displaying the radon concentration chart of a virtual campaign.

      • validateCampaign

        protected boolean validateCampaign()
        Validates the selected campaign. Only returns true if a simulation object is selected and among the seven room-comboboxes one cellar and six normal rooms are selected.
        Returns:
        True if 6 rooms and 1 cellar is selected.
